## Join to a referral program

> Headers

```
Content-type: application/json
```

> Body example

```json
{
    "shop_id": "...",
    "shop_secret": "...",
    "identifier": "PHONE",
    "id": ...
}
```

> Request example

```shell
curl --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
  --request POST \
  --data-binary "@data.json" \
  https://<%= config[:api_endpoint] %>/loyalty/referral/join
```

> The above command returns JSON structured like this:

```json
{
  "status": "success",
  "payload": {
    "code": "..."
  }
}
```

Adds a person to a referral program. Works only if the user is joined to loyalty program before.

### HTTP Request


`POST https://<%= config[:api_endpoint] %>/loyalty/referral/join`
### Query Parameters

| Parameter   | Required | Description               |
|-------------|----------|---------------------------|
| shop_id     | true     | Your API key              |
| shop_secret | true     | Your API secret key       |
| identifier  | true     | User's phone (identifier) |
| id          | true     | Referral program ID       |





